		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think I know why a front loader is brighter..
<br />
<br />I cracked opened the silver box and traced the video line.  It seems that there is a C1740 transistor inside of it!  Yet another video amp!
<br />
<br />OH.. and the 3rd party schematics out there are wrong.   <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=":wink:" title="Wink" />

		

