	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've decided to drill holes in my top loader because I've also done the stereo mod.  So I needed a total of 3 jacks.  Plus, I strongly suggest that you have you RCA jacks as far away from where the old RF connector is.  You want to minimize the amount of noise you pick up from the power supply.  It tends to be the nosiest section in the system.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
